long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Engage in thrilling soccer matches using your oversized head! Heads Arena: Soccer All Stars presents an opportunity for you to showcase your skills as you represent one of the 13 top-tier teams boasting remarkable soccer-headed players. Whether you prefer solo challenges, one-on-one showdowns, or engaging in two-on-two battles, this game has it all. Step into the world of head soccer, select your beloved football club, and embark on a quest to conquer the tournament and emerge victorious!
